        "created_at": "2022-11-27T22:38:21.671Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Nice bottles\u2013just polished a tranche of '85 du Tertre I had sourced. Drank beautifully and I am now on to some 2001. Seems to be an underrated and classic producer. Still?</p>",
        "post_number": 4,
